OL,5, The government's flagship green heating
OL,6, scheme has been described as "seriously
OL,7, failing" by a Lords inquiry.           
OL,9,FThe Boiler Upgrade Scheme grants       
OL,10,Fhouseholds #5,000 to help switch from a
OL,11,Fgas boiler to a low-carbon heat pump.  
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, the Lords Net Zero       
OL,14,FCommittee said grant take-up is so low 
OL,15,Fthe national target for green heating  
OL,16,Fis "very unlikely to be met".          
OL,18,FThe government responded by saying it  
OL,19,Fwould launch a marketing campaign to   
OL,20,Fmake people more aware of the scheme.  
